		"ItemTooltips"
		{
			"item_pipe"		"Purchase if no other support is buying it."
			"item_aether_lens"		"Aether Lens lets Vengeful Spirit use her ultimate, Magic Missile and Wave of Terror at an even larger range with amplified damage. This allows her to initiate even better or scout areas from an even safer distance without risk."
			"item_force_staff"		"Surprise swaps would work especially well with this item. In addition, swapping then Force Staff your way back is a good way to have your cake and eat it too!"
			"item_solar_crest"		"Solar Crest is the next logical step after Medallion of Courage that really synergizes with Vengeful Spirit's armour debuff. To add, it adds a miss effect that can be used for to allies for evasion or enemies.

Solar Crest can be used both offensively and defensively."
			"item_heavens_halberd"		"Heaven's Halberd is a comfortable item that adds to Vengeful Spirit's survivability and puts her ultimate in a less crisis of a situation."
			"item_glimmer_cape"		"Glimmer Cape is an alternative utility item that can work alongside Force Staff to provide further escape after Swapping an enemy or simply to save an ally."
			"item_ghost"		"Ghost Scepter is to help you versus physically carries that want to immediately target you. This prevents them from targeting you and let's you escape via Force Staff or other items that provide your escape."
			"item_spirit_vessel"		"Spirit Vessel is a great end-game item versus especially tanky heroes or those with a lot of health."
			"item_sphere"		"Consider Linken's Sphere if specific ultimate, target abilities like stuns and silences are keeping you down. This should be seen different as Black King Bar because it will waste ultimate abilities on you like Doom's Doom or Necrophos' Reaper Scythe from completely killing/disabling you."
			"item_medallion_of_courage"		"Medallion of Courage works great alongside Vengeful Spirit's Wave of Terror for an early Roshan or ganks. Medallion of Courage can be used both offensively or defensively (improving an allies' armour). 

Use Wave of Terror to scout out fogged areas or to break channeled consumables (Clarity/Bottle)"
			"item_ultimate_scepter"		"Aghanim's allows you to cast abilities with your ghost form after you die in a fight."
		}
	}
