			"special_bonus_all_stats_8"		"The extra stats has more applicability throughout the game and as a support/utility hero like Vengeful Spirit to alleviate some mana issues, survivability and damage output as Vengeful Spirit's auto-attack is pretty decent."
			"vengefulspirit_magic_missile"		"Magic Missile during the early-phase of the game helps you initiate onto enemies with a guaranteed stun.

Later on, this will be your follow-up with your ultimate ability: Nether Swap, which will hold enemies in place after you swap them towards your allies' locations."
			"vengefulspirit_wave_of_terror"		"Wave of Terror should not be used in the lane phase otherwise you may push the lane too hard. Consider using it to illuminate areas you can't see, to weaken enemy heroes, etc.

Use your ability to easily stack camps, disrupt Clarity and Healing Salves."
			"vengefulspirit_nether_swap"		"Nether Swap an ally or an enemy to ensure ideal positioning or to save an ally:

1. Target an enemy with Nether Swap
2. Follow-up with Magic Missile
3. Simultaneously use Glimmer Cape or Force Staff to retreat back
4. Wave of Terror as your allies kill the foe"
